---
import LandingLayout from '../layouts/LandingLayout.astro';
---

<LandingLayout title="Free Website Preview for Your Business" description="Squatch Marketing builds a preview of your website first. You see the work before you commit. $149/mo, first month free, cancel anytime.">

  <!-- HERO -->
  <section class="relative min-h-[90vh] flex items-center gradient-mesh noise overflow-hidden">
    <div class="orb-drift absolute top-[10%] left-[5%] w-[600px] h-[600px] rounded-full bg-blue/[0.09] blur-[160px] pointer-events-none"></div>
    <div class="orb-drift-reverse absolute bottom-[8%] right-[0%] w-[500px] h-[500px] rounded-full bg-teal/[0.07] blur-[140px] pointer-events-none"></div>

    <div class="relative z-10 max-w-5xl mx-auto px-6 lg:px-8 pt-28 lg:pt-32 pb-16">
      <div class="reveal mb-6">
        <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-3.5 py-1.5 rounded-xl bg-teal/[0.08] border border-teal/[0.12]">
          <div class="w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-teal animate-pulse"></div>
          <span class="text-teal text-xs font-semibold tracking-wide">First Month Free</span>
        </div>
      </div>

      <h1 class="reveal reveal-delay-1 font-display font-800 text-[clamp(2.5rem,6vw,5rem)] text-white leading-[1.05] tracking-[-0.03em] mb-6">
        We build your website first. <span class="text-gradient">You decide if you want it.</span>
      </h1>

      <p class="reveal reveal-delay-2 text-lg sm:text-xl text-white/50 leading-relaxed max-w-2xl mb-10">
        No templates. No DIY headaches. Tell us about your business and we'll send you a fully branded preview site within 5 business days. If you love it, we launch it on your domain for $149/mo. If you don't, walk away.
      </p>

      <div class="reveal reveal-delay-3 flex flex-wrap gap-3 mb-12">
        <a href="/request-demo?ref=websites" class="btn-gradient px-8 py-4 rounded-xl text-white font-semibold text-[15px]">
          <span>Get Your Free Preview</span>
        </a>
        <a href="#how-it-works" class="btn-ghost px-8 py-4 rounded-xl text-white/50 hover:text-white font-medium text-[15px]">
          How It Works
        </a>
      </div>

      <div class="reveal reveal-delay-4 flex flex-wrap items-center gap-8">
        <div>
          <div class="text-3xl font-display font-800 text-gradient">13+</div>
          <div class="text-xs text-white/30 mt-1">Preview sites built</div>
        </div>
        <div class="w-px h-10 bg-white/[0.08]"></div>
        <div>
          <div class="text-3xl font-display font-800 text-white">5 days</div>
          <div class="text-xs text-white/30 mt-1">From brief to live preview</div>
        </div>
        <div class="w-px h-10 bg-white/[0.08]"></div>
        <div>
          <div class="text-3xl font-display font-800 text-gradient">$0</div>
          <div class="text-xs text-white/30 mt-1">Risk to try</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="absolute bottom-0 left-0 right-0 h-32 bg-gradient-to-t from-void to-transparent pointer-events-none z-10"></div>
  </section>

  <!-- HOW IT WORKS -->
  <section id="how-it-works" class="relative py-24 bg-void overflow-hidden">
    <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="reveal mb-12 text-center">
        <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-3.5 py-1.5 rounded-xl bg-blue/[0.08] border border-blue/[0.12] mb-5">
          <div class="w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-blue animate-pulse"></div>
          <span class="text-blue text-xs font-semibold tracking-wide">How It Works</span>
        </div>
        <h2 class="font-display font-800 text-3xl sm:text-4xl text-white leading-tight">
          Three steps. <span class="text-gradient">Zero risk.</span>
        </h2>
      </div>

      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-5">
        <div class="reveal glass-interactive rounded-2xl p-7">
          <div class="font-display font-800 text-5xl text-gradient mb-4">1</div>
          <h3 class="font-display font-700 text-lg text-white mb-3">Tell us about your business</h3>
          <p class="text-white/40 text-sm leading-relaxed">5-minute intake. Your services, your brand, what you want customers to feel. Share existing photos or we use high-quality stock.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="reveal reveal-delay-1 glass-interactive rounded-2xl p-7">
          <div class="font-display font-800 text-5xl text-gradient mb-4">2</div>
          <h3 class="font-display font-700 text-lg text-white mb-3">We build your preview</h3>
          <p class="text-white/40 text-sm leading-relaxed">Within 5 business days we deliver a fully branded, live preview site. Your business name, services, content, and visual identity. Not a mockup, an actual site you can click through.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="reveal reveal-delay-2 glass-interactive rounded-2xl p-7">
          <div class="font-display font-800 text-5xl text-gradient mb-4">3</div>
          <h3 class="font-display font-700 text-lg text-white mb-3">You decide</h3>
          <p class="text-white/40 text-sm leading-relaxed">Love it? We launch on your domain, handle hosting, and you get monthly updates for $149/mo. Don't love it? Walk away, no hard feelings. First month is always free.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <div class="section-divider"></div>

  <!-- WHAT'S INCLUDED -->
  <section class="relative py-24 bg-void overflow-hidden">
    <div class="orb-drift absolute top-[20%] right-[-5%] w-[400px] h-[400px] rounded-full bg-blue/[0.04] blur-[120px] pointer-events-none"></div>

    <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-[1fr_1.2fr] gap-12 items-start">
        <div class="reveal">
          <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-3.5 py-1.5 rounded-xl bg-teal/[0.08] border border-teal/[0.12] mb-5">
            <div class="w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-teal animate-pulse"></div>
            <span class="text-teal text-xs font-semibold tracking-wide">What You Get</span>
          </div>
          <h2 class="font-display font-800 text-3xl sm:text-4xl text-white leading-tight mb-6">
            Everything your business <span class="text-gradient">actually needs.</span>
          </h2>
          <p class="text-white/40 text-base leading-relaxed">
            Not a template. Not a builder. A real custom-coded site on the same stack we use for our agency. Fast, secure, and designed around converting visitors into customers.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="space-y-3">
          <div class="reveal glass-interactive rounded-xl p-5 flex items-start gap-4">
            <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-lg bg-blue/[0.1] border border-blue/[0.15] flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0">
              <span class="text-blue font-bold">1</span>
            </div>
            <div>
              <div class="font-semibold text-white mb-1">Custom 4-8 page site</div>
              <div class="text-white/40 text-sm">Home, Services, About, Contact. More pages as needed. All hand-coded, not dragged-and-dropped.</div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="reveal reveal-delay-1 glass-interactive rounded-xl p-5 flex items-start gap-4">
            <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-lg bg-blue/[0.1] border border-blue/[0.15] flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0">
              <span class="text-blue font-bold">2</span>
            </div>
            <div>
              <div class="font-semibold text-white mb-1">Mobile-first responsive</div>
              <div class="text-white/40 text-sm">50%+ of your traffic is mobile. Your site is built for thumbs first, then scaled up to desktop.</div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="reveal reveal-delay-2 glass-interactive rounded-xl p-5 flex items-start gap-4">
            <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-lg bg-blue/[0.1] border border-blue/[0.15] flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0">
              <span class="text-blue font-bold">3</span>
            </div>
            <div>
              <div class="font-semibold text-white mb-1">Cloudflare hosting + SSL</div>
              <div class="text-white/40 text-sm">Sub-second page loads. SSL included. 99.99% uptime. We handle all the infrastructure.</div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="reveal reveal-delay-3 glass-interactive rounded-xl p-5 flex items-start gap-4">
            <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-lg bg-blue/[0.1] border border-blue/[0.15] flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0">
              <span class="text-blue font-bold">4</span>
            </div>
            <div>
              <div class="font-semibold text-white mb-1">Monthly content updates</div>
              <div class="text-white/40 text-sm">New services, photos, seasonal copy. Send us the changes, we update the site same-week.</div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="reveal reveal-delay-4 glass-interactive rounded-xl p-5 flex items-start gap-4">
            <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-lg bg-blue/[0.1] border border-blue/[0.15] flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0">
              <span class="text-blue font-bold">5</span>
            </div>
            <div>
              <div class="font-semibold text-white mb-1">Google Analytics + reporting</div>
              <div class="text-white/40 text-sm">You see exactly who's visiting, where they came from, and what they did. Real data, not vanity metrics.</div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <div class="section-divider"></div>

  <!-- PRICING -->
  <section class="relative py-24 section-mesh overflow-hidden">
    <div class="orb-drift absolute top-0 left-[30%] w-[500px] h-[500px] rounded-full bg-teal/[0.05] blur-[140px] pointer-events-none"></div>

    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="reveal glass-strong rounded-3xl p-10 sm:p-12 text-center relative overflow-hidden">
        <div class="absolute top-0 left-0 w-1/3 h-1/2 bg-gradient-to-br from-blue/[0.06] to-transparent pointer-events-none rounded-3xl"></div>

        <div class="relative z-10">
          <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-3.5 py-1.5 rounded-xl bg-teal/[0.08] border border-teal/[0.12] mb-6">
            <div class="w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-teal animate-pulse"></div>
            <span class="text-teal text-xs font-semibold tracking-wide">Pricing</span>
          </div>

          <div class="flex items-baseline justify-center gap-2 mb-3">
            <span class="font-display font-800 text-6xl sm:text-7xl text-white">$149</span>
            <span class="text-white/40 text-xl">/mo</span>
          </div>
          <p class="text-white/50 text-base mb-8">First month free. No contracts. Cancel anytime.</p>

          <div class="grid sm:grid-cols-2 gap-3 text-left mb-10 max-w-md mx-auto">
            <div class="flex items-center gap-2 text-white/60 text-sm">
              <span class="text-teal">✓</span> Custom website
            </div>
            <div class="flex items-center gap-2 text-white/60 text-sm">
              <span class="text-teal">✓</span> Hosting + SSL
            </div>
            <div class="flex items-center gap-2 text-white/60 text-sm">
              <span class="text-teal">✓</span> Monthly updates
            </div>
            <div class="flex items-center gap-2 text-white/60 text-sm">
              <span class="text-teal">✓</span> Analytics included
            </div>
            <div class="flex items-center gap-2 text-white/60 text-sm">
              <span class="text-teal">✓</span> First month free
            </div>
            <div class="flex items-center gap-2 text-white/60 text-sm">
              <span class="text-teal">✓</span> Cancel anytime
            </div>
          </div>

          <a href="/request-demo?ref=websites" class="btn-gradient px-10 py-4 rounded-xl text-white font-semibold text-[15px] inline-block">
            <span>Get Your Free Preview</span>
          </a>
          <p class="text-white/25 text-xs mt-4">No credit card required to see your preview.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <div class="section-divider"></div>

  <!-- FAQ -->
  <section class="relative py-24 bg-void overflow-hidden">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="reveal mb-10 text-center">
        <h2 class="font-display font-800 text-3xl sm:text-4xl text-white leading-tight">
          Common <span class="text-gradient">questions</span>
        </h2>
      </div>

      <div class="space-y-3">
        <div class="reveal glass-interactive rounded-xl p-6">
          <div class="font-semibold text-white mb-2">What's the catch with the free preview?</div>
          <p class="text-white/40 text-sm leading-relaxed">There isn't one. We build a real site for you. If you like it, we launch it for $149/mo. If you don't, we've wasted some of our time. Low-pressure, no games.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="reveal reveal-delay-1 glass-interactive rounded-xl p-6">
          <div class="font-semibold text-white mb-2">Do I own the site?</div>
          <p class="text-white/40 text-sm leading-relaxed">While you're subscribed, yes, it runs on your domain and is yours to use. If you cancel, we take the site offline after 30 days. Want the code? $500 one-time fee and it's yours to self-host.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="reveal reveal-delay-2 glass-interactive rounded-xl p-6">
          <div class="font-semibold text-white mb-2">Can you match our existing branding?</div>
          <p class="text-white/40 text-sm leading-relaxed">Yes. Send us your logo, colors, and any brand guidelines. If you don't have any, we'll build visual direction based on your industry and personality.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="reveal reveal-delay-3 glass-interactive rounded-xl p-6">
          <div class="font-semibold text-white mb-2">What if I want more than a 4-8 page site?</div>
          <p class="text-white/40 text-sm leading-relaxed">Custom quote. E-commerce, booking systems, blogs, member portals — we can build them. Base plan covers most small businesses but we scope bigger projects individually.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="reveal reveal-delay-4 glass-interactive rounded-xl p-6">
          <div class="font-semibold text-white mb-2">How quickly can my site go live?</div>
          <p class="text-white/40 text-sm leading-relaxed">Preview within 5 business days of your intake form. If you approve and hand off your domain, we can launch within another 1-2 business days.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- FINAL CTA -->
  <section class="relative py-20 bg-void overflow-hidden">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-6 lg:px-8 text-center">
      <h2 class="reveal font-display font-800 text-3xl sm:text-4xl text-white leading-tight mb-6">
        Ready to see what yours could look like?
      </h2>
      <p class="reveal reveal-delay-1 text-white/50 text-lg mb-8">
        5-minute intake. Free preview. Zero pressure.
      </p>
      <a href="/request-demo?ref=websites" class="btn-gradient px-10 py-4 rounded-xl text-white font-semibold text-[15px] inline-block">
        <span>Get Your Free Preview</span>
      </a>
    </div>
  </section>

</LandingLayout>
